Sports personality, Walter Mokoena, wed his long term girlfriend in an intimate and elite ceremony this past weekend in Pretoria. The SABC sports anchor wed Nosizwe Vuso, at a private ceremony which saw President Jacob Zuma, amongst others, in attendance. Vuso regards President Jacob Zuma as her father after Zuma raised both she and her twin sister. Mokoena, who has a daughter with Pearl Thusi, and Vuso have been dating for the past three years and have a child together. &nbsp; &nbsp; Pictures sourced from Zkhiphani.com For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter. &nbsp;